        "action": "VAT Complete Removal.",
        "additional_details": "1. VAT was introduced with EU membership, now Brexit complete the UK taxpayers deserve such income back.\r\n2. VAT is often added on top of already taxed goods like fuel.\r\n3. Covid and fuel crisis are problems that make it more evident that increasing/returning VAT to the taxpayers will help.",
